  "texts": [
    "The codebook also plays a key role in deductive research with LLMs.",
    "A feature of ChatGPT's chat interface is its ability to keep a record (i.e., memory) of the chat conversation and learn from the different inputs within the specific conversation.",
    "The logic is similar to that of an interview guide for a semi-structured or thematic interview.",
    "It may take several questions to be reformulated to capture the observation of interest to the researcher.",
    "Hence, the codebook for such a classification task is pivotal in the iterative prompting process."
